Class CollectionsCustom

  • java.lang.Object
    • szakacs.kpi.fei.tuke.misc.CollectionsCustom

  • public class CollectionsCustom
extends java.lang.Object
    A class providing custom read-only wrapper views of our custom Stack and Queue collections.

    • Method Detail

      • unmodifiableStack

        public static <T> Stack<T> unmodifiableStack(Stack<T> stack)

        Returns an unmodifiable view of the stack passed to it as argument.

        Calling push() or pop() on this view causes an UnsupportedOperationException to be thrown.

        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of elements in the original stack and the read-only view.
        Parameters:
        stack - the stack for which to create a read-only view.
        Returns:
        a read-only view of the stack passed as argument.

      • unmodifiableQueue

        public static <T> Queue<T> unmodifiableQueue(Queue<T> queue)

        Returns an unmodifiable view of the queue passed to it as argument.

        Calling enqueue() or dequeue() on this view causes an UnsupportedOperationException to be thrown.

        Type Parameters:
        T - the type of elements in the original queue and the read-only view.
        Parameters:
        queue - the queue for which to create a read-only view.
        Returns:
        a read-only view of the queue passed as argument.
